title: Someone Was Waiting
description: In this Dateline classic, detectives in Frisco, Texas uncover a series of suspects after a woman is found dead in her garage -- all of them connected in different ways to her complicated and secretive life. Josh Mankiewicz reports. Originally aired on NBC on December 9, 2016.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
